OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776059756
OL,3,CI Am Maximus wins Grand National for
OL,4,Csecond time
OL,6,FI Am Maximus became the first horse
OL,7,Fsince Red Rum to win two Grand
OL,8,FNationals, as Willie Mullins also
OL,9,Fbecame the first trainer since Vincent
OL,10,FO'Brien in the 1950s to win three
OL,11,Fsuccessive races.
OL,13,FIn a race with plenty of early drama
OL,14,Fthat saw last year's third Grangeclare
OL,15,FWest part company with Patrick Mullins
OL,16,Fat the first, and Panic Attack fall at
OL,17,Fthe third, I Am Maximus kept to the
OL,18,Finside path he knows so well in the
OL,19,Fhands of Paul Townend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
