PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776059756
OL,3,CI Am Maximus wins Grand National for
OL,4,Csecond time
OL,6,FThe 10-year-old horse was a favourite
OL,7,Ffor this year's race after losing to
OL,8,FNick Rockett last year.
OL,10,FIt was a record fourth win in the race
OL,11,Ffor I Am Maximus's owner, JP McManus,
OL,12,Fwho also saw his Iroko go two places
OL,13,Fbetter than last year for second.
OL,14,FJordans was third, with Johnnywho
OL,15,Ffourth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
