FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776059756
OL,3,CI Am Maximus wins Grand National for
OL,4,Csecond time
OL,6,FMullins, who joins Red Rum's trainer
OL,7,FGinger McCain and Fred Rimell as a
OL,8,Ffour-time National-winning handler,
OL,9,Fsaid: "He's a superb horse who got a
OL,10,Ffantastic ride and I think the most
OL,11,Ftrouble he got was from his
OL,12,Fstablemates and his co-pilots, they
OL,13,Fdidn't give him much room."
OL,15,F"It is (hard to win off top-weight),
OL,16,Fbut maybe the modern-day National is
OL,17,Fchanging and we're looking at it a bit
OL,18,Fdifferently.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
