OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776059756
OL,3,CI Am Maximus wins Grand National for
OL,4,Csecond time
OL,6,F"It's the race we aspire (to win).
OL,7,FIt's the race you want to win and be a
OL,8,Fpart of ` just to have a runner is a
OL,9,Ftremendous sensation.
OL,11,F"He is just a superstar ` nothing
OL,12,Ffazes him. He comes out, does what he
OL,13,Fhas to do and wins Nationals."
OL,15,FAsked if he thought I Am Maximus could
OL,16,Ffurther emulate Red Rum with a
OL,17,Fhistoric third success next year,
OL,18,FMullins said: "I thought the horse ran
OL,19,Fa cracker last year, he just got
OL,20,Fbeaten, hopefully he'll be here next
OL,21,Fyear."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@^O]zD@OOU
