PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776059756
OL,3,CI Am Maximus wins Grand National for
OL,4,Csecond time
OL,6,FA delighted Townend said: "He's tough,
OL,7,Fisn't he? He'll gallop to the end of
OL,8,Fthe world for you.
OL,10,F"He still probably didn't travel with
OL,11,Fthe enthusiasm of the first year, but
OL,12,FI just thought the cheekpieces helped
OL,13,Fin the middle part of the race.
OL,15,F"I saw the one that went in front, but
OL,16,FI wasn't going to be the one chasing
OL,17,Fhim, I had enough going OK in front of
OL,18,Fme and I was able to get a lead to the
OL,19,Felbow."
OL,26,@nD@[OUrD@AOUwD@AOU{D@GO]
